<div>You can assign the PR to someone (and assign a milestone and labels) *after* you create it. &nbsp;This is different than Trac where you could set the title, body, and all those values and *then* create the ticket.</div>
<div><br>
</div>
<div>See&nbsp;<a href="https://github.com/open-mpi/ompi/wiki/SubmittingBugs">https://github.com/open-mpi/ompi/wiki/SubmittingBugs</a> for a little more detail.</div>
